plicit $p=3$ results in Groisser et al. (2017). Addressing the\nuniqueness-related questions requires a thorough understanding of the fiber\nstructure of $M(p)$, which we also provide.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Feb 2017 16:18:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Dec 2017 15:06:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-22"}
