roposed estimation method based on\nrealization theory, finding that despite stringent constrains on the allowed\nnoise level, exact dimension estimation can still be achieved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Feb 2017 18:42:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Jul 2017 19:26:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 3 Jan 2018 17:32:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-04"}
