ical cases, and explicitly characterize the optimal controls for the case\nof linear objective functions in closed form. Finally, we see that, in the\ncanonical example of designing an election campaign, identifying late-deciders\nis a critical component in the optimal design.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Feb 2017 15:45:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Jul 2018 00:11:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-25"}
